    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly calibrated double-VANOS system. This chassis has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, sending power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, and the exterior retains a factory-fresh luster with no evidence of oxidative stress or paint depth variance. A mechanically pristine specimen for the enthusiast who demands peak performance and structural perfection.",
